name: Walla Walla Mobile Units
notes:
This clinic will be held on the Walla Walla Community College campus at the Student Rec Center. The clinic will offer PFIZER COVID-19 VACCINE for all qualifying individuals aged 12 years & over and JOHNSON & JOHNSON COVID-19 VACCINE for all qualifying individuals aged 18 years & older. 
Parental/Guardian consent is required for 12 – 17 years old, parent/guardian consent and signature can be completed on-site or in the final screen of the online registration process. 
Appointments are recommended but Walk-ins are welcome!
Masks are required. If you do not have a mask, one will be provided.
We look forward to seeing you. Thanks for keeping Walla Walla well.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

notes:

Those under 18 must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via video/phone call or paper format.
